      <pubDate>Fri, 24 May 2024 10:32:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧佩克+将会议改为线上，官员们预计石油减产时间将延长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-24/opec-to-hold-next-month-s-meeting-online-rather-than-in-vienna</link>
      <description><![CDATA[OPEC+将在网上而非现场举行下个月的政策会议，而几位代表表示，他们预计该组织将当前的减产措施延长至今年下半年。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-24/opec-to-hold-next-month-s-meeting-online-rather-than-in-vienna</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 24 May 2024 07:48:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>农作物指数抹去 2024 年损失，食品通胀担忧再度升温</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-24/crop-index-erases-2024-loss-rekindling-food-inflation-worries</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于恶劣天气引发了人们对小麦和咖啡等收成的担忧，并再次引发了人们对食品价格上涨的担忧，主要农作物指数消除了 2024 年的损失。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-24/crop-index-erases-2024-loss-rekindling-food-inflation-worries</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 24 May 2024 05:53:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
